divs: sighting detailsi had decided to take the trash out to the bin in the backyard. looked at the clear night sky a few times while i was out, to see if the starlike objects i see occasionally were present. there was no apparent activity i could see. i than decided to acknowledge from my personal experience that the starlike objects are known to appear no matter where i am, so i asked for a sign and went inside to warm up. some minutes later i went outside on the back deck and looked up to see one starlike object flying over from east to west, approximately above 5,000 ft, no nav\strobe lights, just white\starlike. i held up my hand and waved. a separate quick starlike flash of light occurred some distance behind and aside from the westbound object. this sighting did not cause any distress, i always find it fascinating and exciting to see these flying objects.
Summary: The night sky was clear. No UFOs in sight. I asked for a sign. A flyby soon appeared.
